           SHORT="A utility to access/tune Linux's EIDE drivers"

cat << EOF
hdparm is a shell utility to access/tune ioctl features of the Linux
hard disk and (E)IDE drivers for kernel 1.3.61+. Its primary use is for
enabling irq-unmasking and IDE multiplemode.
EOF
